{"tid":501543,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[純回憶]仲記得當年出iphone","createTime":"2017-12-17T03:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T07:10:13.000Z","uid":131208,"like":106,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1a03352e168ca8e20dac1a0da65576959fa49a8b","tid":501543,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"果陣係2011年1月<br />\n我電話plan就到期，所以趁機出左iphone 4 plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲記得當時iphone 4缺貨缺得好勁<br />\n連訂台機都要等兩三個禮拜先有貨，係一月既時間喎，已經唔係開賣果期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能果年smart phone仲未十分普及<br />\n所以出左機後幾撚威威呀<br />\nd同學見到我部機直頭係雙眼發光<br />\n「嘩有米仔」，「好有生活態度」等回應此起彼落<br />\n囡囡仲hi哂手請哂波餅咁求我借部機比佢玩fruit ninja同mega jump<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起真係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年後換5s，果時smart phone已經好普及<br />\n所以d fd都冇咩大反應，但始終都係第一部64 bit<br />\n速度上真係屌打哂所有旗艦機<br />\n好彩果時睇清楚個spec先換機<br />\n唔係就貪平換濕鳩5c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後今年換埋8 plus，人生第3部smart phone<br />\nd fd既反應已經唔同哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「喂屌你明明同7冇分別做咩要咁死蠢換8呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n「嘩咁大部既係咪X黎架？」<br />\n雖然我唔知呢個咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大概而家只剩返欷歔蒼桑既感覺..."},{"pid":"b5b458e3c283374a4e9039150896ba31c1581664","tid":501543,"uid":23874,"like":29,"dislike":9,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死<br />\n屌你老味你班ifandog清醒啲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1fa05f12dd51c3f638b11c2179d22fccff3612","tid":501543,"uid":52068,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣係2011年1月<br />\n我電話plan就到期，所以趁機出左iphone 4 plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲記得當時iphone 4缺貨缺得好勁<br />\n連訂台機都要等兩三個禮拜先有貨，係一月既時間喎，已經唔係開賣果期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能果年smart phone仲未十分普及<br />\n所以出左機後幾撚威威呀<br />\nd同學見到我部機直頭係雙眼發光<br />\n「嘩有米仔」，「好有生活態度」等回應此起彼落<br />\n囡囡仲hi哂手請哂波餅咁求我借部機比佢玩fruit ninja同mega jump<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起真係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年後換5s，果時smart phone已經好普及<br />\n所以d fd都冇咩大反應，但始終都係第一部64 bit<br />\n速度上真係屌打哂所有旗艦機<br />\n好彩果時睇清楚個spec先換機<br />\n唔係就貪平換濕鳩5c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後今年換埋8 plus，人生第3部smart phone<br />\nd fd既反應已經唔同哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「喂屌你明明同7冇分別做咩要咁死蠢換8呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n「嘩咁大部既係咪X黎架？」<br />\n雖然我唔知呢個咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大概而家只剩返<span style=\"color: red;\">欷歔</span>蒼桑既感覺...</blockquote><br />\n唏噓<br />\nbtw用手機都可以搞到個人唏噓蒼桑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d671ab3b58b5a42dcbbd649ed339c091d3ed2117","tid":501543,"uid":34793,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"屌 手機都可以攞黎打飛機 思考人生 廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f105cec12cb35648d04d2473f486d3667bd197ca","tid":501543,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:53:00.000Z","msg":"太耐冇寫過文<br />\n唔識埋尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4484a2d7e719154955952eceaa9acb5950d0a0","tid":501543,"uid":12705,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"Iphone4 真係型到仆街, 又耐用, 用左4年<br />\n無叉過尿袋<br />\n上堂玩推銀機 mega jump, d同學提子到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre